# Project Structure  
- Root directory: `root/`  
- `apps/landing/` → Vite + React + TS + Tailwind (port 5173)  
- `apps/auth/` → Node.js + Express (port 3001)  
- `apps/portal/` → Vite + React + TS + Tailwind (port 5174)  
- `apps/forum/` → Node.js + Express (port 3002)  
- `apps/api/` → Node.js + Express (port 4000)  
- `nginx/makesoft.conf` → Nginx reverse proxy  
- `docker-compose.yml` controls all services including MongoDB container  
- `.env` & `docker/` sub-folders for infra
